 put and agreed to. Resolved, That the Committee has considered the draft European Union (Definition of Treaties) (Association Agreement) (Central America) Order 2018. draft European Union (Definition of Treaties) (Political Dialogue and Cooperation Agreement) (Cuba) Order 2018 Resolved, That the Committee has considered the draft European Union (Definition of Treaties) (Political Dialogue and Cooperation Agreement) (Cuba) Order 2018.— (Sir Alan Duncan.)     Share           3.04 pm          Committee rose.                     ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
