. I am grateful to him and thank him for enabling me to be present in spirit, if not in the flesh. Question put and agreed to.     Share           10.01 am          Adjourned accordingly till Wednesday 18 July at Ten o’clock.                     ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
